  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Cut the zucchini, bell peppers, onion, and mushrooms into large chunks.",
    "In a large bowl, mix together smoked paprika, French seasoning, olive oil, lemon juice, mulukhiyah, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the vegetables to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Thread the marinated vegetables onto skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
